vwr.project.voidbubble.domain.world
Class Entity

java.lang.Object
  vwr.project.voidbubble.domain.world.Entity

public class Entity
extends java.lang.Object

Entity contains all the values specific to a certain object. These values are unique to the individual entity, even if they are the same type of object.
